[6.6](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/process-engine-6-6)

[6.7](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/process-engine-6-7)

**File:** calculate_advanced.ipd

**Shows:** Activities, input and output mappings, process parameters

**Components:** Start Element, Mapping Element, urlWriter Activity, End Element, Connection

**Process parameters:** a, b, url

An extension of the Calculate example. In addition to the calculation, the result is written to a url using the urlWriter Activity. The url and the values for the calculation need to be provided as parameters when executing the process.
